### v02 — /next-hand Regression (S7 Cycle 8 #341)
###
### S7 Cycle 8 Wave 1 신규 시나리오 (2026-05-12, issue #341).
### v02-2-hand-flow.http (Cycle 6 PR #320) 위에 **N round 일반화 회귀** 추가.
###
### 본 시나리오는 v02 baseline 의 0→1→2→3 점 검증을 6-seat round-robin 으로
### 확장하여 invariant 기반 회귀 강화한다.
###
### 검증 invariants (POST /api/session/{id}/next-hand):
###   INV-1: handNumber strict +1 per call
###   INV-2: dealerSeat strict +1 mod seats (round-robin stride)
###   INV-3: isDealer uniqueness (정확히 1명)
###   INV-4: per-seat reset (currentBet=0, status=active)
###   INV-5: community + pot reset
###   INV-6: stack 보존
###   INV-7: sessionId 불변
###
### 의존성:
###   - S8 Cycle 5 PR #301 (#287) Engine harness POST /next-hand endpoint
###   - S9 Cycle 6 PR #320 v02 baseline
###
### 실행:
###   - REST Client / curl 으로 step-by-step
###   - Playwright: v02-next-hand-regression.spec.ts (자동화)
###
### Out-of-scope:
###   - SB/BB 위치 검증 (toJson 비노출)
###   - Hand 2+ 실제 play-through (blinds 미게재)
###   - BO/Lobby/CC UI (Engine-only smoke)

@engine = http://localhost:18080

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase A: Setup — 6-seat NL Holdem session
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### A.1 GET /health
GET {{engine}}/health

### A.2 POST /api/session — 6-seat 세션 생성
# @name initSession
POST {{engine}}/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant": "nlh",
  "seats": 6
}

# Assertion:
#   - sessionId matches /^[a-z0-9]+$/
#   - dealerSeat === 0, handNumber === 0
#   - seats.length === 6

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase B: Hand 1 hand_end (auto-rotate baseline)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### B.1 POST event — hand_end (Hand 1 즉시 종료, fold 없이 baseline rotate)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{initSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "hand_end"
}

# Assertion (baseline):
#   - handNumber === 1 (0 → 1, hand_end 자동 +1)
#   - dealerSeat === 1 (0 → 1, hand_end 자동 +1)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase C: /next-hand × 6 (round-robin 완주)
#
# 각 호출마다 INV-1 (handNumber +1) + INV-2 (dealer +1 mod 6) 검증.
# 6-seat 테이블이므로 6회 호출 후 dealer 가 1 → 2 → 3 → 4 → 5 → 0 → 1
# round-robin 1바퀴 완주 + 다음 1단계 위치 = dealer 1 복귀.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### C.1 POST /next-hand — Round 1 (handNumber 1→2, dealer 1→2)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{initSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 2, dealerSeat === 2
#   - seats[2].isDealer === true, others false
#   - community === [], pot.main === 0
#   - 모든 seats[].currentBet === 0, status === active

### C.2 POST /next-hand — Round 2 (handNumber 2→3, dealer 2→3)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{initSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 3, dealerSeat === 3
#   - seats[3].isDealer === true

### C.3 POST /next-hand — Round 3 (handNumber 3→4, dealer 3→4)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{initSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 4, dealerSeat === 4

### C.4 POST /next-hand — Round 4 (handNumber 4→5, dealer 4→5)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{initSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 5, dealerSeat === 5

### C.5 POST /next-hand — Round 5 (handNumber 5→6, dealer 5→0, wraparound)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{initSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 6, dealerSeat === 0 (5+1=6 mod 6 = 0 wraparound)
#   - seats[0].isDealer === true

### C.6 POST /next-hand — Round 6 (handNumber 6→7, dealer 0→1)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{initSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 7, dealerSeat === 1 (round-robin 1바퀴 완주 후 +1)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase D: 최종 누적 검증
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### D.1 GET /api/session/{id} — 최종 상태
GET {{engine}}/api/session/{{initSession.response.body.sessionId}}

# DoD Assertion:
#   - sessionId 불변 (INV-7)
#   - handNumber === 7 (누적 hand_end +1 + nextHand × 6 = 7)
#   - dealerSeat === 1 (round-robin 1바퀴 완주)
#   - 6 seats 모두 active
#   - 모든 seats[].currentBet === 0
#   - community === [], pot.main === 0
#   - 모든 seats[].stack === 1000 (fold/award 없이 hand_end 만이므로 보존)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Definition of Done (v02 next-hand regression)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# - [x] Engine harness :18080 가동 시 모든 step HTTP 200/201
# - [x] handNumber 단조 증가 (1 → 7), strict +1 per call
# - [x] dealer round-robin (1 → 2 → 3 → 4 → 5 → 0 → 1), +1 stride 일관
# - [x] 6-seat wraparound (dealer 5 → 0) 정상 동작
# - [x] sessionId 불변 across 6 calls
#
# Out-of-scope:
#   - SB/BB 위치 검증 (toJson 비노출)
#   - Hand 2+ 실제 play (별도 hand_start trigger 필요)
#   - WebSocket broadcast 검증 (v99 영역)
#
# 본 시나리오 작성 + 실행 검증: 2026-05-12 S7 Cycle 8 Wave 1 (issue #341)
